比分析，深入分析成本变动的根本原因；根据标准成本与实际成本之间的差异分析等因素，追踪到业务相关方并进一步推动改进和优化。\n2. 对生产/运营相关的费用（物料消耗、能耗、维修费）等进行监控、预警，确保支出的合理受控，识别关键的成本解决机会，并推动公司的降本增效。\n3. 与各个业务团队深入交流并密切合作，理解第一手的业务信息，从产品的全生命周期进行成本跟踪，并从端到端的视角分析成本，从而寻找整体最优的的成本解决方案。\n4. 采购合同的审批与归档。\n5. 领导交办的其他相关事宜。","requirement":"1. 本科及以上学历，财务、经济类相关专业。\n2. 3年以上财务相关经验，其中必须有制造业成本核算或成本BP经验。\n3. 较强的数据分析、数据处理能力，熟练使用EXCEL等办公工具。\n4. 高度的责任心，做事细心、认真，有较强的抗压能力。\n5. 较强的跨部门沟通、协调能力。","job_category":null,"city_info":null,"recruit_type":{"id":"101","name":"全职","en_name":"Full-time","i18n_name":"全职","depth":2,"parent":{"id":"1","name":"社招","en_name":"Experienced","i18n_name":"社招","depth":1,"parent":null,"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"publish_time":1763691472775,"job_hot_flag":null,"job_subject":null,"code":null,"department_id":null,"job_function":null,"job_process_id":"7154705446175033607","recommend_id":null,"city_list":[{"code":"CT_11","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","location_type":null,"i18n_name":"北京","py_name":null,"mdm_code":null,"node_status":null}],"job_post_info":{"id":null,"job_id":null,"title":null,"sub_title":null,"address_id":null,"address":null,"city":null,"education":null,"experience":null,"description":null,"requirement":null,"min_salary":null,"max_salary":null,"currency":null,"head_count":null,"crator_id":null,"expiry_time":null,"progress":null,"department_id":null,"job_type":null,"recruitment_type":{"id":"101","name":"全职","en_name":"Full-time","i18n_name":"全职","depth":2,"parent":{"id":"1","name":"社招","en_name":"Experienced","i18n_name":"社招","depth":1,"parent":null,"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"job_process_time":null,"job_in_charge_user_id":null,"biz_create_time":null,"HighlightList":null,"JobChannelPublishList":null,"required_degree":null,"never_expiry":null,"job_hot_flag":null,"subject":null,"sequence":null,"min_level":null,"max_level":null,"job_post_object_value_map":{},"code":null,"job_active_status":null,"job_process_type":null,"biz_modify_time":null,"job_function":null,"job_process":null,"job_process_id":null,"job_category":null,"address_list":[{"id":"7537645455594160132","name":"北京市海淀区中关村东路1号院7号楼威盛大厦7层","en_name":"","district":{"district_code":"DS_2","name":"海淀区","en_name":"Haidian","i18n_name":"海淀区"},"city":{"city_code":"CT_11","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","i18n_name":"北京","py_name":"beijing"},"state":{"state_code":"ST_8","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","i18n_name":"北京"},"country":{"country_code":"CN_1","name":"中国大陆","en_name":"Chinese Mainland","i18n_name":"中国大陆"},"i18n_name":"北京市海淀区中关村东路1号院7号楼威盛大厦7层","active_status":1}],"city_list":null,"correlation_job_list":null,"tag_list":null,"department":null,"job_storefront_mode":null,"storefront_list":null,"target_major_list":null,"schema":null,"job_post_process_time_list":null,"job_level_id_list":null},"storefront_mode":1,"storefront_list":null,"process_type":1},{"id":"7573601627207141674","title":"技术产品经理","sub_title":null,"description":"1.\t前沿调研与竞品分析\n\t•\t跟踪国内外开源/商用灵巧手方案及关键零部件的技术进展，包括触觉传感器、关节模组、芯片方案等\n\t•\t分析竞品的架构方案、性能参数、集成策略，并输出内部参考材料\n\t2.\t供应链调研与能力认证（Qualify）\n\t•\t开拓并评估核心器件供应商，建立对触觉模组、关节模组、SoC芯片的选型机制\n\t•\t与技术/采购团队合作，推动样品评估、打样验证与合格供应商清单建立\n\t3.\t产品需求定义与跨部门协作\n\t•\t主导产品需求评估与关键技术特性定义，协调结构、控制、嵌入式、算法、系统等多个团队评审需求可行性\n\t•\t撰写高质量的PRD文档与功能规格书，定义关键性能指标（如触觉响应带宽、关节反驱力矩精度等）\n\t4.\t项目进度管理与技术评审参与\n\t•\t配合项目管理团队，参与关键阶段评审（EVT、DFT、DFM、试产等），保障产品开发进度与关键技术决策质量\n\t5.\t性能-成本-质量的全局平衡管理\n\t•\t协调研发、运营、供应链、测试等各方，确保产品在成本、质量、性能三方面取得平衡与突破\n\t6.\t上市前的应用测试与demo设计指导\n\t•\t设计标准化测试用例，推动仿真 + 实物联合测试（DexUMI，Sim2Real验证等）\n\t•\t指导产品应用工程师完成Demo搭建、测试方案验证、问题复盘与结果验收\n\t7.\t上市前的SBOM，规格书，以及产品\n        8.      上市后的产品维护与迭代\n\t•\t收集、整理来自市场与应用一线的改进建议，进行功能变更评估、版本管理与需求复用设计","requirement":"教育背景\n机械工程、自动化、机器人、电子工程、计算机或相关专业本科及以上学历\n工作经验\n有3年以上复杂机电系统/机器人/智能硬件产品经验；有灵巧手、机械臂、关节模组、传感器类经验者优先\n技术视野\n理解灵巧手系统组成（结构、执行器、感知、控制、通信等），能快速学习新技术并落地为产品指标\n跨界协作\n有与研发/结构/算法/嵌入式/供应链多方协同的经验，具备优秀的需求协调和技术评审沟通能力\n文档能力\n能独立撰写产品需求文档、功能规范、供应商能力评估表、测试计划等交付物\n\n\n\n加分项：\n- 有过从0到1，参与硬件设计到量产，再到交付的经验；\n- 熟悉传感器，PID控制，力控等经验；\n- 海外留学或者工作经验；","job_category":null,"city_info":null,"recruit_type":{"id":"101","name":"全职","en_name":"Full-time","i18n_name":"全职","depth":2,"parent":{"id":"1","name":"社招","en_name":"Experienced","i18n_name":"社招","depth":1,"parent":null,"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"publish_time":1763366740658,"job_hot_flag":null,"job_subject":null,"code":null,"department_id":null,"job_function":null,"job_process_id":"7154705446175033607","recommend_id":null,"city_list":[{"code":"CT_11","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","location_type":null,"i18n_name":"北京","py_name":null,"mdm_code":null,"node_status":null}],"job_post_info":{"id":null,"job_id":null,"title":null,"sub_title":null,"address_id":null,"address":null,"city":null,"education":null,"experience":null,"description":null,"requirement":null,"min_salary":null,"max_salary":null,"currency":null,"head_count":null,"crator_id":null,"expiry_time":null,"progress":null,"department_id":null,"job_type":null,"recruitment_type":{"id":"101","name":"全职","en_name":"Full-time","i18n_name":"全职","depth":2,"parent":{"id":"1","name":"社招","en_name":"Experienced","i18n_name":"社招","depth":1,"parent":null,"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"job_process_time":null,"job_in_charge_user_id":null,"biz_create_time":null,"HighlightList":null,"JobChannelPublishList":null,"required_degree":null,"never_expiry":null,"job_hot_flag":null,"subject":null,"sequence":null,"min_level":null,"max_level":null,"job_post_object_value_map":{},"code":null,"job_active_status":null,"job_process_type":null,"biz_modify_time":null,"job_function":null,"job_process":null,"job_process_id":null,"job_category":null,"address_list":[{"id":"7537645455594160132","name":"北京市海淀区中关村东路1号院7号楼威盛大厦7层","en_name":"","district":{"district_code":"DS_2","name":"海淀区","en_name":"Haidian","i18n_name":"海淀区"},"city":{"city_code":"CT_11","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","i18n_name":"北京","py_name":"beijing"},"state":{"state_code":"ST_8","name":"北京","en_name":"Beijing","i18n_name":"北京"},"country":{"country_code":"CN_1","name":"中国大陆","en_name":"Chinese Mainland","i18n_name":"中国大陆"},"i18n_name":"北京市海淀区中关村东路1号院7号楼威盛大厦7层","active_status":1}],"city_list":null,"correlation_job_list":null,"tag_list":null,"department":null,"job_storefront_mode":null,"storefront_list":null,"target_major_list":null,"schema":null,"job_post_process_time_list":null,"job_level_id_list":null},"storefront_mode":1,"storefront_list":null,"process_type":1},{"id":"7571785644297521459","title":"Linux系统软件及BSP驱动工程师","sub_title":null,"description":"岗位职责\n1.负责机器人算力单元Linux系统配置、裁剪及优化，构建可量产的系统镜像与发布流程；\n2.负责机器人算力单元 SoC 板级支持包（BSP）开发与维护：U-Boot、设备树、内核配置、驱动适配与稳定性优化;\n3.负责Linux系统外设驱动（Ethernet/EtherCAT、PCIe、USB、SPI、I2C、Uart、CAN/CAN-FD、GPIO等接口，Camera、Audio、4G/5G、Wifi、蓝牙等功能模块）开发与调试；\n4.负责算力单元系统性能（可靠性、实时性等）优化（调度/中断优化、实时性能提升、PTP时间同步、系统资源隔离与保护等），支持机器人算法、应用在整机上的部署调试；\n5.支撑算力单元控制器量产方案开发（OTA方案、故障诊断与处理、安全性能提升、产线下线流程等）；\n6.负责解决机器人研发、量产过程中出现的Linux系统相关问题。","requirement":"任职要求\n1.本科及以上学历，三年以上嵌入式Linux内核/BSP/驱动开发经验；\n2.精通 C/C++、Shell，熟悉Python用于脚本与产测；\n3.至少熟悉英伟达、地平线、瑞芯微、高通等SOC芯片中的一种，熟悉其linux系统软件或驱动开发框架；\n4.熟悉 Linux 内核与驱动模型、设备树、常见总线协议与调试方法；\n5.有Linux系统裁剪配置、性能分析经验（dma、irq、调度、内存等分析及瓶颈定位）；\n6.具有板级硬件联调能力（示波器、逻辑分析仪等总线分析工具），了解基本的EMC、ESD；\n7.熟练使用Git等版本管理工具，具有良好跨团队沟通协作能力。\n加分项\n1.具有NVIDIA Orin/Thor等机器人算力单元/运动控制单元平台开发量产经验；\n2.具有ROS 2底层适配、实时执行器、零拷贝通信、DDS 配置优化经验；\n3.具有高带宽外设与存储开发调试经验：MIPI-CSI、V4L2、NVMe、PCIe调试；\n4.具有RTOS 协同（FreeRTOS等RTOS）与异构多核（A-core/M-core）通信开发调试经验；\n5.有GPU 加速开发经验。","job_category":null,"city_info":null,"recruit_type":{"id":"101","name":"全职","en_name":"Full-time","i18n_name":"全职","depth":2,"parent":{"id":"1","name":"社招","en_name":"Experienced","i18n_name":"社招","depth":1,"parent":null,"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"children":null,"active_status":1,"selectability":1},"publish_time":1762943891043,"job_hot_flag":null,"job_s